wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: Wellspring church of Wake Forest NC. Bible-based, sharing the love of Jesus Christ. We believe that God is a Father to all. He wants us to accept his free gift of salvation for the work Jesus did for all on the cross. We are a community church who love each other, serve each other, and stand with each other.
